 Version 3.0 - Also allows the SysOp  to leave msg  attached to the above!

 Version 3.1 - Some minor changes, etc. Also allows those who you want axs
               to the sysop menu (eg: co-sysop) via user_msg.axs.

 Version 3.2 - Some minor changes & updates.  Allows the sysop to lock out
               unwanted users and also give sysop menu axs to users.

 Version 3.5 - Optimised code, added extra screens, changed the layout and
               other small changes.

 Version 3.6 - Time for an update (last version). A few small changes.

